  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invade, Build and Defend! Complete the campaign for a Steam leader-board position!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the invading forces to defeat the allies. Defend your position by building and earning shrapnel. Destroy enemy ships in sea battles, bomb enemy positions and defeat the enemy boss blimps! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoyed playing this game (or not), check out my other game Zombie Quest (Early Access) available on Steam now :)</p>",
